data.description: New to the Market!  The “Brooks” Floor Plan built by Premier Builder Award Winning Paran Homes, is DEFINITELY A MUST SEE!  Bay Creek Manor Subdivision boasts Quality Built Homes in an established community with low HOA fees.   Location is Everything, and this GEM is conveniently situated in close proximity to shopping, Bay Creek Park and Award Winning Grayson Schools.  Upon entry prepare to be amazed at the 2 story foyer with a balcony view from the upstairs hallway.  Altogether this spacious home boasts 6 Bedrooms, 4 Bathrooms, In-Law Suite on the main floor,  crown molding and trim throughout, Granite Counter tops, Gas Fireplace, 42 inch Maple Cabinets in Kitchen,  Breakfast area with breakfast bar overlooking into the family room, Separate Family Room, Living Room, Separate Dining Room with coffered ceilings and gorgeous arched doorway entries.  On the Upper Floor, you are met with 5 Bedrooms, an over-sized Primary Suite that hosts a spa-like bathroom with  separate vanities, tub with custom accents, separate shower and ample closet space!  The secondary bedrooms have vaulted ceilings, generous storage and natural light.  Enjoy the fully fenced back yard and patio area, for peaceful evenings at home. Make this house your home today!
